   "source": [
    "# KNN Classifier for penguins\n",
    "\n",
    "The following exercise aims to apply a KNN classifier to distinguish different species of penguins based on the Palmer Penguins dataset imported via Seaborn."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "93dbc562",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### 1) Import libraries"
